        <abstract>
            <p>Edmond Perrier of Paris would be pleased to receive earthworms collected in Venezuela.</p> 
<p>CD fears that he exaggerated the importance of worms in forming ledges on hillsides [see <hi rend="italic">Earthworms</hi>, p. 278 ff.].</p> 
        </abstract>
